USAir Group Inc said it is reducingcoach fares up to 62 pct between Atlanta and 21 destinationsfor travel April 12 through June 15.    The fares are non-refundable and applicable to roundtripflights. Reservations must be made at least two days in advanceand tickets purchased within 24 hours after reservations aremade, the company said.    Roundtrip fares between Atlanta and Pittsburgh, forexample, would be 178 dlrs instead of 478 dlrs, USAir said. Reuter&#3;